description: Bublar Group AB engages in the provision and publication of software and mobile games. The company is headquartered in Stockholm, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2017-11-06. The company combines two core technologies during development of games: augmented reality (AR) and location-based services (LBS). The technologies are integrated within location-based software platform. Additionally, the Company focuses on areas of eye tracking, haptics, natural user interfaces and real-time three-dimensional visualization/simulation.
